<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Raspadinha Digital</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; text-align: center; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
        h1 { color: #ff5d00; }
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 100px); gap: 15px; justify-content: center; margin: 30px auto; max-width: 350px; }
        .cell { 
            width: 100px; height: 100px; background-color: #333; color: white;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; 
            cursor: pointer; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 12px;
            transition: all 0.2s; box-shadow: 0 4px 0 #000;
        }
        .cell:hover { background-color: #444; }
        .cell.revealed { 
            background-color: #fff !important; 
            color: #ff5d00; 
            border: 2px solid #ff5d00; 
            box-shadow: none;
            transform: translateY(4px);
            font-size: 18px; /* Ajuste para caber a palavra */
        }
        #message { 
            margin: 30px auto; max-width: 500px; display: none; 
            padding: 25px; border: 3px solid #ff5d00; border-radius: 20px;
            background-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        button { background: #ff5d00; color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 25px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 15px; font-size: 16px; }
        button:hover { background: #e05200; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Tenta a tua sorte! 🍀</h1>
    <p>Escolhe <b>3 números</b> para raspar:</p>

    <div class="grid" id="grid">
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)">1</div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)">2</div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)">3</div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)">4</div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)">5</div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)">6</div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)">7</div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)">8</div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)">9</div>
    </div>

    <div id="message">
        <h2>🎉 PARABÉNS! 🎉</h2>
        <p>Acabaste de ganhar a obrigatoriedade de fazer um contrato <strong>Repsol</strong> hoje!</p>
        <button onclick="window.location.reload()">Jogar Novamente</button>
    </div>

    <script>
        let count = 0;
        function reveal(element) {
            if (!element.classList.contains('revealed') && count < 3) {
                element.classList.add('revealed');
                element.innerText = 'REPSOL';
                count++;

                if (count === 3) {
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        document.getElementById('message').style.display = 'block';
                        document.getElementById('grid').style.pointerEvents = 'none'; 
                    }, 500);
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
